Details
_____________________________________________________________________________________

The FireGem hair will bring a splash of Unusual into your content. Designed to work with the Genesis 2 Female(s) and Genesis 3 Female(s) it comes with additional pearl and ornamental curl jewelry for both the scalp and the braided parts.

To get you started we have included a handful of styling presets and utility poses. A selection of eight basic materials and eight effect materials for the hair plus four materials for both jewelry types is also included. On top of that you get a huge choice of beautiful ShoXoloR materials, both for the full hair, partial materials and the jewelry.
